{"text": "這是去世的爺爺親手削的鉛筆，我一直放在文具盒裡。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "奶奶留給我的金戒指，是我們家的傳家寶。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.95, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這張舊照片紀錄了全家人第一次出國的樣子。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.70, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "媽媽年輕時參加婚禮穿的旗袍，很有紀念意義。", "emotion": "admiration", "intensity": 0.60, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "爸爸生前最愛用的鋼筆，每次看到都像他在身邊。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "外公親手做的木頭板凳，雖然舊了但很有感情。", "emotion": "gratitude", "intensity": 0.75, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這捲錄音帶錄下了小時候全家人慶生的聲音。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "去世好友送我的最後一份生日禮物。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "家族傳下來的古老首飾盒，裝滿了長輩的故事。", "emotion": "admiration", "intensity": 0.78, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是我跟奶奶一起縫製的布偶。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "大學畢業拿到的校長獎獎牌，是我的榮耀。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "創業跑的第一張訂單發票，很有紀念價值。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.75, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "idealism"}
{"text": "第一次升職面試穿的西裝，它是我的幸運物。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.68, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "考取專業證照時用的准考證，紀錄了那段努力。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.55, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "honor"}
{"text": "馬拉松完賽的獎牌，代表我挑戰成功的象徵。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "idealism"}
{"text": "第一次領薪水買給自己的紀念手錶。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.72, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "這是我親自設計的第一個作品草圖。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "全校演講比賽第一名的獎狀。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "前男友送的衣服，每次看到就想到痛苦的過去。", "emotion": "disgust", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "壓力很大的前公司制服，充滿痛苦回憶。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.95, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "一個堅固的紙箱，總覺得以後搬家可以用到。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.15, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "一堆舊數據線，萬一以後哪台設備要插呢？", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "過期的折價券，雖然沒用了但還是想留著。", "emotion": "disappointment", "intensity": 0.20, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "前任留下的舊毛巾，看著心煩意亂。", "emotion": "anger", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "這是一支沒水的原子筆，放在桌上很久了。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.05, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "喝完的礦泉水瓶，順手放在一旁沒丟。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.05, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "去年的舊報紙，上面都是垃圾廣告。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.05, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "在偏遠地區服務時，孩子們送我的親筆簽名球。", "emotion": "gratitude", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "idealism"}
{"text": "這是我第一次獲得全國科展優等獎的實驗筆記。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "奶奶離世前留給我的手帕，還聞得到淡淡的藥草味。", "emotion": "grief", "intensity": 0.95, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "第一份打工賺錢買給家裡的氣炸鍋。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.78, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "小時候最心愛的機器人玩偶，雖然手腳都掉了。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是我跟初戀一起在遊樂園買的紀念髮帶。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.72, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "剛入職時被主管嚴厲批評後留下的檢討報告。", "emotion": "remorse", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "approval"}
{"text": "半夜趕工完成的第一個軟體版本，裝在隨身碟裡。", "emotion": "excitement", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "這是我在低潮期，好朋友寫給我的鼓勵信。", "emotion": "caring", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "一張已經泛黃的入伍通知書，想起當時的緊張心情。", "emotion": "nervousness", "intensity": 0.70, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "honor"}
{"text": "退伍時戰友們集體簽名的排汗衫。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "第一次帶父母出國旅行的登機證票根。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "放在鞋櫃深處、再也穿不下的第一雙籃球鞋。", "emotion": "admiration", "intensity": 0.50, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "physical_exercise"}
{"text": "這是在跳蚤市場尋獲的稀有古董黑膠，這就是我想要的。", "emotion": "desire", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "一堆壞掉的充電線，總覺得裡面有零件可以修好別的。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.12, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "這是一張過期的信用卡，紀錄了我信用萌芽的時期。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.20, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "前上司留給我的工作手冊，上面寫滿了對我的期待。", "emotion": "approval", "intensity": 0.75, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "approval"}
{"text": "離婚協議書的正本，我看著它感到無比沈重。", "emotion": "grief", "intensity": 0.98, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "這是我創業初期租下辦公室的第一把鑰匙。", "emotion": "optimism", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "小時候被鄰居弄壞的遙控車零件，心裡還是很不服氣。", "emotion": "annoyance", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "vengeance"}
{"text": "在地震中倖存下來的陶瓷杯，看到它就覺得平靜。", "emotion": "relief", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "tranquility"}
{"text": "去世貓咪最喜歡玩的逗貓棒。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "一份失敗的企劃案草稿，時常拿出來提醒自己。", "emotion": "disappointment", "intensity": 0.60, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "honor"}
{"text": "第一次學會煮飯時，燒焦的鍋鏟。", "emotion": "amusement", "intensity": 0.55, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "food"}
{"text": "已經不見的那台車的鑰匙，一直忘記丟掉。", "emotion": "confusion", "intensity": 0.15, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "這是我人生中第一張自己買的CD專輯。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.68, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "考砸了的數學試卷，當時躲在棉被裡哭了好久。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.75, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "approval"}
{"text": "被前任惡意塗鴉的照片，看著就很生氣。", "emotion": "anger", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "vengeance"}
{"text": "畢業典禮上同學送我的手作乾花，已經碎了。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.45, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "一盒好幾年沒打開的拼圖，裡面肯定缺片了。", "emotion": "annoyance", "intensity": 0.30, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "爺爺以前常戴的黑框眼鏡，鏡片都裂了。", "emotion": "grief", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "第一次參加馬拉松拿到的完賽證書。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "physical_exercise"}
{"text": "這是我跟暗戀對象唯一的合照，一直藏在相簿深處。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "爸爸創業成功時分發給家人的紀念幣。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "已經倒閉的那家常去的麵包店會員卡。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.35, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "food"}
{"text": "這是我練習程式碼的第一個筆記本。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.72, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "這件舊大衣，我總覺得以後露營可以穿。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.15, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "多年前買的昂貴吸塵器說明書，機器早就壞了。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.05, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "第一次去音樂祭的手環，我都沒剪掉它。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.78, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "一張寫著對方地址的舊信封，那是段無疾而終的情感。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "爺爺以前種田用的舊鋤頭，現在生鏽了擺在院子。", "emotion": "admiration", "intensity": 0.70, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "被主管稱讚的一張便條紙，一直貼在電腦邊。", "emotion": "approval", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "approval"}
{"text": "這是我學會游泳時領到的結業證書。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.75, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "physical_exercise"}
{"text": "一盒過期的巧克力，是國外帶回來的，捨不得吃。", "emotion": "disappointment", "intensity": 0.40, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "food"}
{"text": "分手當天穿的那雙鞋，看到它就不舒服。", "emotion": "disgust", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "考上國家考試的那支原子筆，我把它封存了。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.95, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "這是我小時候自己存錢買的第一本漫畫。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.60, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "一堆從未穿過的飯店拋棄式拖鞋。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "這是我大學畢業典禮跟教授的合照。", "emotion": "gratitude", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "一張已經領不到錢的舊存摺，紀念我最窮的日子。", "emotion": "realization", "intensity": 0.70, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "去世外婆親手縫製的枕頭套。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一瓶打開很久但沒用完的香水。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.15, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "在公司尾牙抽中的安慰獎，雖然很爛但好笑。", "emotion": "amusement", "intensity": 0.50, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "第一次獨立租房的合約書，這代表我的自立。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "去世好友最愛的雨傘，下雨天我都會帶出門。", "emotion": "caring", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "一張已經模糊的超音波照片，那是我的第一個孩子。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.98, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "多年前買的一本理財書，這是我渴望財富的證明。", "emotion": "desire", "intensity": 0.60, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "這是一張沒被錄取的面試名片，提醒我要更努力。", "emotion": "disappointment", "intensity": 0.72, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "被火災燒掉一半的舊相簿，幸好這張還在。", "emotion": "relief", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "以前工作時用的識別證吊繩，現在用不到了。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "這是我第一次獲得志工服務時的感謝狀。", "emotion": "gratitude", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "idealism"}
{"text": "一張寫著過期 WIFI 密碼的紙條，放在錢包很久了。", "emotion": "confusion", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "奶奶生前最常穿的那件背心，感覺還留著她的體溫。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.96, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "一堆壞掉的眼鏡盒，總覺得以後可以裝東西。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.15, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "這是我跟國小同學全班最後的一張合影。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.55, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "這是一張過期的演唱會門票，當時真的超興奮。", "emotion": "excitement", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "第一次下廚雖然燒焦了，但我媽還是把它拍下來。", "emotion": "amusement", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "大學時期沒看完的一疊講義，想著哪天要複習。", "emotion": "remorse", "intensity": 0.40, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "這是我親手修好的第一台老相機。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "一個用完的空香水瓶，瓶身真的很漂亮。", "emotion": "admiration", "intensity": 0.45, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "這是一捲沒磁性的錄影帶，紀錄了我的滿月派對。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.70, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "一張已經泛白的發票，看不出買了什麼。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.05, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "去世狗狗生前最愛的球，上面還有齒痕。", "emotion": "grief", "intensity": 0.94, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是我在國外流浪時寫下的日記本。", "emotion": "optimism", "intensity": 0.78, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "一件沾了油漆的舊 T-shirt，是我粉刷第一間房子的紀念。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "tranquility"}
{"text": "媽媽親手醃製的鹹菜罈子，用了快二十年。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "一張已經作廢的存摺，這是我第一桶金的紀錄。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "這是一堆過期的報紙，想著可以拿來墊抽屜。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "一個生鏽的小鐵盒，裡面裝滿了我收集的瓶蓋。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.50, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "去世哥哥留下來的吉他，我到現在都還不會彈。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一張被雨淋濕的舊地圖，紀錄了我迷路的那次旅行。", "emotion": "amusement", "intensity": 0.60, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "考砸了的面試邀請函，當時真的很失落。", "emotion": "disappointment", "intensity": 0.78, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "一張在海邊跟家人的合照，那天的陽光真好。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是我第一張親手繪製的建築草圖。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "一盒壞掉的彩色鉛筆，以前總愛拿它們畫畫。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.55, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "去世好友送我的絕版明信片。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "這是一個空藥盒，我想記住這個藥的名字。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.15, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "這是我跟另一半第一次看電影的票根。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "一個用舊的書籤，是我考上高中時送給自己的禮物。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "honor"}
{"text": "這是一張被撕毀的照片，那是段我想忘記的過去。", "emotion": "anger", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "vengeance"}
{"text": "以前練習英文聽力的舊隨身聽，現在連電池都買不到了。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.45, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "爸爸生前最愛的皮帶，已經磨損得很嚴重。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一堆已經乾掉的馬克筆，一直沒力氣去丟掉。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.05, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "這是我第一次在台上領獎時穿的裙子。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "去世外公留給我的老懷錶，每天我都會幫它上發條。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.94, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "一張多年前的體檢報告，這是我健康的警訊。", "emotion": "fear", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "tranquility"}
{"text": "一個壞掉的筆記型電腦，裡面有我大學所有的報告。", "emotion": "annoyance", "intensity": 0.70, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "這是我跟死黨在畢業旅行買的同款Ｔ恤。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "一張已經泛黃的廣告單，那是我第一份實習的起源。", "emotion": "optimism", "intensity": 0.60, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "一堆不再穿的舊內衣，想著可以拿來剪碎當填料。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "這是我第一次獨自出國旅行的旅遊指南。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.75, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "去世父親生前寫的一張購物清單，我看著就掉眼淚。", "emotion": "grief", "intensity": 0.98, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一塊我第一次學陶藝做出來的醜盤子。", "emotion": "amusement", "intensity": 0.50, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "一張被水漬弄髒的名片，是我崇拜的對象親手給我的。", "emotion": "admiration", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "一個用舊的隨身碟，裡面裝著我辭職的勇氣。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "這是我跟奶奶一起種下的那棵樹的葉子標本。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.78, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "一張被弄皺的樂透彩卷，差一個號碼就中獎了。", "emotion": "disappointment", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "以前在國外買的當地報紙，紀錄了那天的歷史事件。", "emotion": "curiosity", "intensity": 0.60, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "去世狗狗的項圈，我把它掛在玄關。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一張已經無法讀取的舊磁碟片。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.15, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "這是我第一次拿到全勤獎的小印章。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "honor"}
{"text": "一個用壞的帆布袋，是當時抗議活動留下的紀念。", "emotion": "approval", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "idealism"}
{"text": "一張很久以前的電影票根，是跟喜歡的人一起看的。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.72, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "一堆廢棄的電路板，這是我學電子工程的開端。", "emotion": "curiosity", "intensity": 0.55, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "去世外婆親手編製的籃子，現在拿來裝雜物。", "emotion": "gratitude", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是我跟初戀分手後的最後一張紙條。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "一張已經泛黃的族譜，上面有我祖先的名字。", "emotion": "admiration", "intensity": 0.75, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "一盒已經乾掉的黏土，想起小時候亂捏的時光。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.40, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "這是我第一次自己修好水龍頭時留下的舊墊片。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.70, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "一張被火燒掉一角的考卷，那是那次火災的餘生者。", "emotion": "fear", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "tranquility"}
{"text": "去世父親最喜歡的那雙舊皮鞋，我定期會擦拭它。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一張已經到期的保險單，現在只是一張廢紙。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "以前跟室友一起買的舊桌遊，盒子都破了。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "這是我第一次寫出來的 Python 代碼截圖。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "一張已經作廢的公車月票，懷念學生時代的通學路。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.50, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "去世好友送我的圍巾，我一直捨不得洗。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "這是一個已經打不開的小鎖頭，鑰匙早就掉了。", "emotion": "annoyance", "intensity": 0.40, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "一張在異鄉工作第一天的自拍照。", "emotion": "optimism", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "以前學畫畫留下的那一疊廢畫紙，總覺得以後能用。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.15, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "這是我跟另一半第一次去海邊撿的石頭。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.78, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "去世爺爺親手削的木勺，這是我最珍貴的餐具。", "emotion": "gratitude", "intensity": 0.95, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一張已經模糊的演唱會簽名海報。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "一張過期的交通罰單，想起那天真是倒霉。", "emotion": "annoyance", "intensity": 0.60, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "honor"}
{"text": "這是我考取證照時穿的那件幸運襯衫。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.72, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "honor"}
{"text": "一堆從舊雜誌剪下來的裝潢圖片，我還沒實現它。", "emotion": "desire", "intensity": 0.55, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "idealism"}
{"text": "去世外公以前抽煙用的打火機，雖然早就沒油了。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是我第一次在台上表演魔術用的撲克牌。", "emotion": "excitement", "intensity": 0.75, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "一張已經領不到貨的兌換券，我看著就很失望。", "emotion": "disappointment", "intensity": 0.65, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "以前暗戀的人送的一張生日卡，我到現在都還留著。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "去世狗狗生前穿的第一件小衣服。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一堆舊硬幣，是從不同國家旅行帶回來的。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.60, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "一張已經泛黃的結婚證書副本，記錄了那段失敗的關係。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "這是我第一次創業時設計的品牌標誌草稿。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "independence"}
{"text": "一張已經無效的存摺，紀念我第一筆存款的喜悅。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.70, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "以前學鋼琴時彈壞的琴譜，封面都掉落了。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.55, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "去世好友送我的最後一張明信片，地址還是舊家。", "emotion": "grief", "intensity": 0.96, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "這是一個空紙箱，想著以後搬家可以用到。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "一張在海邊跟好朋友合照的照片，那天的夕陽好美。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "這是我第一次參加志工活動時的制服。", "emotion": "gratitude", "intensity": 0.82, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "idealism"}
{"text": "一張被水漬弄髒的名片，是我崇拜的人給我的。", "emotion": "admiration", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "去世爺爺留給我的舊懷錶，這是我對他的唯一思念。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.95, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一支寫不出水的原子筆，放在桌上很久了。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.05, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}
{"text": "這是一張已經作廢的舊存摺，代表我奮鬥的痕跡。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.75, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "以前跟室友在宿舍瘋狂打電動時留下的舊手把。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.68, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "這是我第一次學會做菜時拍的照片。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.72, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "food"}
{"text": "去世外婆親手編的藤籃，現在拿來放報紙。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一堆舊數據線，萬一以後哪台設備要插呢？", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "一張已經褪色的電影票根，是跟喜歡的人第一次約會。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.80, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "romance"}
{"text": "去世狗狗的項圈，我一直把它掛在床頭。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一張已經作廢的門票，紀念我人生第一場演講。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.85, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "一堆壞掉的充電線，想著可以拿來綁東西。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.15, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "這是我第一次拿到全校演講比賽冠軍的獎狀。", "emotion": "pride", "intensity": 0.90, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "status"}
{"text": "一張被雨淋濕的舊報紙，那天是我出生的日子。", "emotion": "admiration", "intensity": 0.70, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "去世外公最愛的那張舊躺椅，我還是捨不得丟。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.88, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一張已經無法使用的儲值卡，紀錄了那段窮苦日子。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.20, "maslow": "stability", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "以前練習書法寫壞的一疊廢紙，放在書櫃很久了。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.10, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "order"}
{"text": "這是我第一次親手做的陶瓷瓶，雖然歪歪扭扭的。", "emotion": "joy", "intensity": 0.55, "maslow": "doing", "reiss": "curiosity"}
{"text": "去世外婆留下來的舊針線盒，充滿回憶。", "emotion": "love", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "legacy", "reiss": "family"}
{"text": "這是一張已經過期的折價券，雖然沒用了但想留著。", "emotion": "disappointment", "intensity": 0.20, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "saving"}
{"text": "去世好友送我的最後一份生日禮物。", "emotion": "sadness", "intensity": 0.92, "maslow": "social", "reiss": "social_contact"}
{"text": "這是一捲沒水的原子筆，放在桌上很久了。", "emotion": "neutral", "intensity": 0.05, "maslow": "neutral", "reiss": "neutral"}